These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
Hobby: chess, gardening, baking, dancing
Pet: snake, rabbit, guinea-pig, hedgehog
Nationality: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
Transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. Nationality:colombian == Pet:hedgehog##1
2. Nationality:indonesian is between Hobby:baking and Hobby:dancing##2
3. Nationality:colombian == Transport:bus##1
4. Transport:trike is on the left of Transport:bus##1
5. Pet:snake is on the left of Nationality:canadian##1
6. Transport:tram == Hobby:baking##1
7. Pet:rabbit is on the left of Hobby:dancing##1
8. Nationality:canadian is on the far right##1
9. Hobby:gardening is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Hobby   | gardening | dancing   | chess  | baking  |
| Pet   | rabbit    | hedgehog    | snake      | guinea-pig    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

